ExecDesc.value: IBM Rational Focal Point RequestAccessController Servlet Information Disclosure

EngDesc.value: An information disclosure vulnerability exists in the IBM Focal Point. The vulnerability is due to input validation error of <italic>file</italic> variable in <italic>com.telelogic.focalpoint.pres.controller.RequestAccessController</italic> servlet. A remote unauthenticated attacker could exploit this vulnerability to read the configuration files of the Webservice Axis Gateway of Focal Point.
